&lt;p&gt;Success in this role is measured by consult-to-start conversion, client satisfaction, and long-term retention. High performers combine empathy and strong judgment with a results orientation — building trust quickly, creating appropriate urgency, and helping families take action with confidence.&lt;/p&gt;
